Revision history for XString

{{$NEXT}}

  [Improvements]
  - Update ppport.h from 3.62 to 3.73 (Devel::PPPort)
  - Add PROTOTYPES: DISABLE to suppress xsubpp warnings on Perl 5.36+

  [Testing]
  - Add trigraph test coverage for all 9 C trigraph sequences
  - Add B::perlstring output comparison to perlstring.t
  - Add UTF-8 test cases for cstring (supplementary planes, multi-byte)
  - Fix perlstring test to properly exercise Latin-1 vs UTF-8 code paths
  - Add vertical tab divergence tests (cstring vs perlstring)
  - Add edge case tests: SV type diversity, boundary conditions, multi-char strings
  - Add thread-safety test (ithreads, skipped when unsupported)
  - Modernize test pragmas and add descriptions to all is() calls

  [CI / Build]
  - Migrate from Travis CI to GitHub Actions
  - Dynamic Perl version matrix via perl-actions/perl-versions (5.8+)
  - Add macOS and Windows CI jobs
  - Enable AUTHOR_TESTING and RELEASE_TESTING on all platforms
  - Fix broken CI badge URLs in POD

  [Documentation]
  - Add CLAUDE.md with developer guide and upstream B.xs sync procedure
  - Add AI policy document (CPAN-AI-POLICY.md)

